        li Top 3% of participants!

    li
      .header
        span.title Pokémon Type Effectiveness Table
        span.time December 2013
      .subheader
        span.languages Python, Regular Expression
      ul
        li Out of frustration with new Pokémon being released and the new Fairy type, I wanted a quick lookup table to know which moves to use against which Pokémon
        li Scrapes the HTML of a web page on #[a(href='http://bulbapedia.bulbagarden.net/wiki/Main_Page') Bulbapedia] with a Regular Expression (knowing full well that HTML is not a regular language!)
        li A Python script uses the parsed data to create a table that shows the effectiveness of every type versus every Pokémon

